The '''High Court of Alderaan''' was the Royal House that presided over the [[Alderaan/Legends|planet's]] [[High Council of Alderaan|High Council]]. From the issue of the [[Alderaan Ascendancy Contention]], the High Court was composed of the members of the [[House of Organa/Legends|Royal House of Organa]].

